Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:53.99,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}認めてた　臆病な過去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:59.91,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}分からないままに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:05.04,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}怖がってた　後ろの自分が現実を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:10.76,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今に映す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:16.09,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}いくつもの空を描いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:20.77,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ここはきっと儚い心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.77,0:01:23.48,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.48,0:01:24.10,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夢で！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:27.90,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}高く飛んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:34.20,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}体はどんな不安まとっても振り払ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:38.62,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}守る　小さな思い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:42.79,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}広がりだして　気づく　弱い私
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:46.62,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}君がいれば　暗い世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:49.54,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}強くいれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:55.22,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}長い夢見る心は　そう　永遠で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:59.39,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:04.68,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I give everything I have
Comment: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OPCH
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:53.99,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}面對過去懦弱的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:59.91,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}即使仍是懵懵懂懂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:10.76,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}害怕如今的自己 身後的映出的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:16.09,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}萬物繪出的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:20.77,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}卻是顆脆弱無比的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.77,0:01:23.48,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}以此為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.48,0:01:24.10,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在夢想中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:27.90,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}展翅高飛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:34.20,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不管身體為多少不安鎖住 都將其拂去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:38.62,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}守住那小小的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:42.79,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}察覺到不斷蔓延的 羸弱的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:49.54,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}若此世有你 堙黯的世界裡我也能堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:55.22,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在無盡的夢裡 我心永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:59.39,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}與君相伴 直至天荒地老
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:04.68,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我將為你 獻出我的所有
